bumblebee (2.4.1-1+git20111102.90e98d2~nattyppa1) natty; urgency=low

  * New upstream snapshot
    - Fix race condition, allowing STOP_SERVICE_ON_EXIT=Y to work when optirun
      is started after another optirun has quit.
    - Detect PCI Bus ID when needed, this should enable detection in case wrong
      ACPI calls hide the device.
    - Fix invalid attempt to unload a driver if none was loaded.

 -- Peter Lekensteyn <lekensteyn@gmail.com>  Wed, 02 Nov 2011 18:31:36 +0100

